# Legend Website Project Rules

## Project Overview
Modern, responsive single-page website for Legendary Hustlers with clean, elegant design and excellent mobile experience.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15.3.3 with TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4
- **UI Components**: Custom components with Tailwind
- **Form Handling**: React Hook Form with file upload
- **Email**: EmailJS for contact form
- **Images**: Next.js Image optimization

## Website Structure
### Single Page Sections (in order):
1. **Hero Section**: Industrial background with navigation
2. **Services Section**: Grid of service cards
3. **Contact Section**: Form with image upload capability
4. **About Us Section**: Team member cards

## Design Requirements
- **Mobile-first responsive design**
- **Clean, industrial aesthetic**
- **Modern typography**
- **Smooth transitions**
- **Professional appearance**
- **Great navigation UX**

## Email Configuration
- Contact form sends to: office@legendaryhustlers.com

## Development Phases
1. **Phase 1**: Foundation & aesthetic (completed)
   - Basic structure and layout
   - Responsive design
   - Content and images
   - Navigation system

2. **Phase 2**: Functionality (completed)
   - Contact form with image upload
   - Email integration
   - Form validation

3. **Phase 3**: Enhancements
   - Performance optimization
   - SEO improvements
   - Accessibility enhancements

## Code Standards
- Use TypeScript for all components
- Follow Next.js 15 app router conventions
- Use Tailwind CSS for all styling
- Create reusable components
- Implement proper SEO tags
- Ensure accessibility (WCAG 2.1)

## Component Structure
```
src/
├── app/
│   ├── page.tsx (main single page)
│   ├── layout.tsx
│   └── globals.css
├── components/
│   ├── ui/ (reusable UI components)
│   ├── sections/ (page sections)
│   └── forms/ (form components)
├── lib/ (utilities)
└── types/ (TypeScript types)
```

## Dependencies
- framer-motion (animations)
- react-hook-form (forms)
- @emailjs/browser (email sending)
- @types/node (file uploads)
- lucide-react (icons)
- zod (form validation)
- clsx & tailwind-merge (utility functions)

## Responsive Breakpoints
- Mobile: 0-768px
- Tablet: 769-1024px
- Desktop: 1025px+

## Color Scheme
- Primary: Industrial grays and metals
- Accent: Yellow/orange highlights
- Background: Diamond plate textures
- Text: High contrast for readability

## Performance Requirements
- Core Web Vitals optimized
- Image optimization
- Lazy loading
- Minimal bundle size
- Fast loading on mobile

## SEO Requirements
- Proper meta tags
- Structured data
- Alt text for images
- Semantic HTML
- Fast loading speeds 